  "reading": "Watch ser vs estar: ‘es aburrido’ (he is boring) is very different from ‘está aburrido’ (he is bored). Keep ‘tengo quince años’ natural: ‘I am fifteen’, not ‘I have fifteen years’.",
  "question": "‘Está en el gimnasio y tiene que entrenar’ =",
