  "readingTitle": "evaluate — Paper 4 — Higher writing: range of tenses",
  "reading": "Top-band answers combine several tenses and structures in one paragraph: a plan (voy a…), a firm future (estudiaré…), a conditional wish (me gustaría…) and, for the very top, the perfect/pluperfect or a subjunctive after ‘es importante que…’.",
  "question": "Which answer shows the widest range of tenses for the top band?",
