  "pageName": "X.2 Reading and Translation into English",
  "source": "mcq",
  "type": "mcq",
  "marks": 1,
  "question": "In the sentence <span data-say=\"Mi madre está embarazada.\">\"Mi madre está embarazada,\"</span> what does <em>embarazada</em> mean?",
